data.text:
David Murray is an actor who played a jumpy thug at the docks in Batman Begins. His character shot his gun around the thugs in an attempt to kill Batman, shouting "where are you?", to which Batman replied "here" and knocked him out. In the Batman Begins novelisation, his character is given the name "Jimmy".
